data.description: Welcome to 1806 Runyan, this nicely updated home holds 4 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms with over 1400 square feet. Located in a quiet established neighborhood close to the main roads as well as Yeso Elementary.  This home would make a great starter home or give you additional rooms for a growing family. There is an area in the back for RV  parking along with a large backyard. This home is ready for you to make it yours today! Give your favorite realtor a call to see it today!
